{"tid":2101340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港大學生校委：教委會指解僱戴耀廷理據「不成立」　仍待校委會作最終決定","createTime":"2020-07-09T16:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T18:19:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2467326ea086f7378578f1171f059969f56fe4e9","tid":2101340,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94-%E6%95%99%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%8C%87%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E4%BB%8D%E5%BE%85%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%25BE%2585%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=318b3d2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%25BE%2585%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%2F&h=b46f6197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94-%E6%95%99%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%8C%87%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E4%BB%8D%E5%BE%85%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學法律系副教授戴耀廷因佔中案被裁定罪成，判監 16 個月。雖然戴耀廷的教席屬於終身制，但校務委員會提出以「好的因由」提出終止聘任即不在此限。如有爭議，個案由教務委員會的「探討充分解僱理由委員會」調查，再交由教委會審理。據香港大學校務委員（本科生代表）李梓成稱，教委會昨晚決定為「不成立」，將只向校務委員會報告其為「misconduct（行為不當）」，惟裁決仍需待校委會最終通過。"},{"pid":"d16868b26e0a55773f45bed8337f5d77090f3423","tid":2101340,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52bbb21e88a2e64a64df32eb1bff7b2a6b66547","tid":2101340,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"戴妖做埋坐監師 份cv 屈晒機<br />\n<br />\n根本唔需要個title<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a664d51326608c3a8171e56395089476973baf","tid":2101340,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feef1b3302a37f1e59ed4517a4a0781ccd123664","tid":2101340,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d52bbb21e88a2e64a64df32eb1bff7b2a6b66547","tid":2101340,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"戴妖做埋坐監師 份cv 屈晒機<br />\n<br />\n根本唔需要個title<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"重點係 雖然佢好柒 但都叫標誌性人物<br />\n係學校搞走佢教席 都係想搞寒蟬效應"},{"pid":"a979dbfe30d661306062e770c